summary = ["The award was also celebrated in Lisbon, where President Jorge Sampaio described it as recognition of Portuguese culture,'' while the local Communist leader, Carlos Carvalho, saw it as a credit to his own party. Saramago's idiosyncratic development of his own resonant style of fiction gives him a high standing  he invokes tradition in a way that in the current state of things can be described as radical,'' the Academy said in the citation for the 76-million kronor dlrs 978,000 prize .In 1995, in the Annual Review of Pharmacology and Toxicology, Furchgott wrote that on May 5, 1978, in the first of a series of planned experiments on arteries from a rabbit, a technician did not follow directions correctly"]